Package: jinx
Title: RLadies+ GitHub Organisation Management
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R:
    person("RLadies+", email = "info@rladies.org", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           comment = c(ROR = "https://ror.org/05wpb1k41"))
Description: GitHub App for managing the RLadies+ organisation. Handles
    onboarding and offboarding of global team members, chapter onboarding,
    PR review automation, org-wide reporting, Airtable sync, website
    automation, chapter monitoring, and interactive issue commands.
Depends: R (>= 4.4.0)
